      <title>瑞士与欧盟重启金融市场监管谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/switzerland-and-eu-resume-talks-on-financial-market-regulation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士与欧盟委员会已恢复有关金融市场监管的讨论，该讨论自 2017 年以来一直处于暂停状态，双方希望达成一项更广泛的协议来管理两国关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/switzerland-and-eu-resume-talks-on-financial-market-regulation</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 16:00:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙在关键投票前保持沉默。他的团队对此心存感激</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/macron-has-gone-quiet-ahead-of-a-key-vote-his-group-is-grateful</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃马纽埃尔·马克龙 (Emmanuel Macron) 上一次公开露面已经是五天前了。而且，在周日第二轮立法投票决定性时刻到来之前，没有迹象表明总统会露面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/macron-has-gone-quiet-ahead-of-a-key-vote-his-group-is-grateful</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 15:57:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民意调查显示勒庞将无法获得法国多数席位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/le-pen-set-to-fall-short-of-majority-in-france-polling-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据三家民意调查公司的预测，玛丽娜·勒庞领导的国民联盟在周日的法国立法选举中将无法获得绝对多数。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/le-pen-set-to-fall-short-of-majority-in-france-polling-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 15:00:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
